"ch09-02-recoverable-errors-with-result.html [randcrate]: "
"https://crates.io/crates/rand [semver]: http://semver.org [cratesio]: "
"https://crates.io/ [doccargo]: https://doc.rust-lang.org/cargo/ "
"[doccratesio]: https://doc.rust-lang.org/cargo/référence/publishing.html "
"[match]: ch06-02-match.html [shadowing]: "
