"     Running `target/debug/variables`\n"
"The value of x is: 5\n"
"The value of x is: 6\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```console\n"
"$ cargo run\n"
"   Compiling variables v0.1.0 (file:///projects/variables)\n"
"    Finished `dev` profile [unoptimized + debuginfo] target(s) in 0.30s\n"
