msgid ""
"Return the `None` value if there is overflow with the `checked_*` methods."
msgstr ""
"Retourner la valeur `None` s’il y a dépassement avec les méthodes "
"`checked_*`."

#: src/ch03-02-data-types.md:137
msgid ""
"Return the value and a Boolean indicating whether there was overflow with "
"the `overflowing_*` methods."
msgstr ""
"Retourner la valeur et un booléen indiquant s’il y a eu dépassement avec les "
"méthodes `overflowing_*`."

#: src/ch03-02-data-types.md:139
msgid ""
"Saturate at the value’s minimum or maximum values with the `saturating_*` "
